caption.text:
Want to never run out of hook ideas? Keep reading! ⤵️

🌟 Hooks are all about CURIOSITY! 🌟

So ask yourself “What part of my Reel could I make someone curious about?”

Maybe it’s the knowledge, maybe it’s the surprise ending, maybe it’s the unpopular opinion, maybe it’s the before and after!

Besides coming up with your own, you should also realize that:

Hooks are EVERYWHERE around you!🌎
• The first line of every chapter.
• The headlines on the news
• The beginnings of other peoples Reels
• The start of your fav movie
• The opening scene of any TV show

But with that being said, I know many of y’all would rather HAVE a fish than LEARN to fish, so here ya go 🐠 Comment HOOK and I'll send ya 25 viral Hook ideas!

caption.text:
Building a biz on social may FEEL lonely, but in reality, we’re all in this together (cue High School Musical dance scene)

It was amazing how almost every creator and their plus one at the @stanforcreators Million Dollar Mastermind this weekend shared identical feelings!!

We’re all in the same boat! 🛶

My tip is to POST about how you’re feeling:
• Struggling with coming up with ideas? Talk about that. 
• Feeling excited about a new project? Post about it. 
• Nervous about the future? That’s a Reel.
• Confused by something? Turn it into a Story.

Don’t worry so much about the FILLINGS (the details of your post) and focus on the FEELINGS!

Do that and I promise you’ll be pleasantly surprised about how NOT alone you are ❤️

text_info_list.text: We’re all feeling the same things.

Even though this whole online business thing can feel lonely,
it’s important to remember that:
Post about what you’re feeling, and you’ll see that you are NOT alone.

caption.text:
I’ve failed…. ☹️

Over the last few months, I’ve been testing out different Stories strategies. 

Finally, I cracked the code & have been consistently getting 50k+ views on my Stories!

sounds good, right? WRONG. ❌

well, maybe 1/2 wrong.

I succeeded in increasing my Story views, which led to more sales, leads, etc.. BUT there was one BIG problem.

My Stories lost their personality. 👎

Yesterday, I got to attend a keynote by @jera.bean at the @stanforcreators Mastermind, where she talked about authenticity & your “secret sauce” — it was a great wake up call.

My Stories have lacked this secret sauce, SO I’M DOING SOMETHING ABOUT IT. ⬇️

I’m going to start incorporating more fun, more life, more joy, more real, MORE ME into my Stories.

My views likely won’t be as high, but that’s not the point. ❤️

The point is a deeper connection with you and being more authentic to myself.

I hope y’all will still tune in ❤️

text_info_list.text: When my Stories are the most authentic
When my Story views are at their highest…

user.full_name: JERA FOSTER-FELL ★ Social Media Educator • Speaker • Coach
Monty Lans | Instagram Strategist & Reels Coach

caption.text:
If you don’t live near these people, keep reading ⤵️

The people you “surround” yourself with can be the people you FOLLOW ON SOCIAL MEDIA!

There is an old saying that “You are the average of your 5 closest friends,” but I think you are also “the average of the 5 people you engage with the most”

Think about the IMPACT of who you follow, watch, and engage with on social media every day!

Ask yourself:
• Who am I engaging with the most?
• What are their values & beliefs?
• Is this creator saying what I WANT to hear or what I NEED to hear?
• How do I feel when I see this persons posts?

Just like you should choose your friends wisely,
I think you should also choose who you follow wisely.

This weekend, I’m lucky enough to be in person with some of the most amazing, inspirational, and impactful creators on the planet at the @stanforcreators Million Dollar Meetup 

During our 2 hour session this morning, I took about 5 pages of notes because of how flipping smart these other creators and business owners are.

Never be the smartest person in the room (or the smartest person you follow lol)

With all of this being said, I hope you consider me someone worth still following. ❤️❤️

If I’m someone who doesn’t challenge you, doesn’t make your life better, or makes you feel worse, then you’re more than welcome to unfollow me ❤️
